  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/563130/extras/e3f8a084b10ada1607858b46d1596572.webp?t=1667176795\" width=500 height=50 /></span><br>Did you ever wonder about the rumors of pushing over cows?<br>Now it´s your turn! Use the darkness and silence of the night to enter<br>the meadows and push over as much cows as possible.<br><br>But be aware of the watchdogs and other dangerous things! <br>Good luck! <br><br>A quite new and interesting gameplay with creepy atmosphere <br>is coming up to you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/563130/extras/a7d4502aabcfdd06bec284cc2d8f15c0.webp?t=1667176795\" width=500 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 15 Levels <br></li><li> Different time limits and number of cows to push over per level <br></li><li> Different kinds of danger to avoid <br></li><li> Dark and creepy atmosphere <br></li><li> Funny and creepy gameplay</li></ul>",
